<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="vi"><head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no" name="viewport"/>
<title>Xác nhận hủy đặt phòng</title>
<!-- Tailwind CSS v3 CDN -->
<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,container-queries"></script>
<style data-purpose="custom-styling">
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f8fbff;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }
    .dotted-line {
      border-top: 1px dotted #cbd5e1;
    }
    /* Fixed bottom container for buttons */
    .fixed-bottom {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      padding: 16px 20px 34px 20px; /* Extra bottom padding for iOS Home Indicator */
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex flex-col">
<!-- BEGIN: Header -->
<header class="bg-white px-4 py-4 flex items-center border-b border-gray-100">
<button aria-label="Back" class="p-1">
<svg class="h-6 w-6 text-gray-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewbox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
<path d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"></path>
</svg>
</button>
<h1 class="flex-1 text-center text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 pr-7">Xác nhận hủy đặt phòng</h1>
</header>
<!-- END: Header -->
<!-- BEGIN: Main Content -->
<main class="flex-1 px-5 pt-10 pb-40 overflow-y-auto" data-purpose="content-scroll-area">
<!-- Warning Icon Section -->
<div class="flex justify-center mb-8">
<div class="w-24 h-24 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" data-purpose="warning-icon-container">
<svg class="h-12 w-12 text-red-600" fill="currentColor" viewbox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
<path d="M12 2L1 21h22L12 2zm0 3.99L19.53 19H4.47L12 5.99zM11 16h2v2h-2v-2zm0-7h2v5h-2V9z"></path>
</svg>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Title and Subtitle -->
<div class="text-center mb-8">
<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 px-4">Bạn có chắc chắn muốn hủy đặt phòng?</h2>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 px-6 leading-relaxed">
        Hành động này không thể hoàn tác sau khi đã xác nhận.
      </p>
</div>
<!-- BEGIN: Booking Info Card -->
<section class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-gray-50 mb-6" data-purpose="booking-info-card">
<div class="mb-4">
<span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider">MÃ ĐẶT PHÒNG</span>
<div class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800">TVY-99218A</div>
</div>
<!-- Separator -->
<div class="dotted-line mb-4"></div>
<!-- Price Rows -->
<div class="space-y-3">
<div class="flex justify-between items-center">
<span class="text-sm text-gray-500">Giá phòng</span>
<span class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-800">280.000đ</span>
</div>
<div class="flex justify-between items-center bg-blue-50 p-3 rounded-xl" data-purpose="refund-highlight">
<span class="text-sm font-medium text-blue-600">Số tiền hoàn lại:</span>
<span class="text-sm font-bold text-blue-600">28.000đ</span>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- END: Booking Info Card -->
<!-- BEGIN: Important Note -->
<section class="bg-gray-100 rounded-2xl p-4 flex gap-3" data-purpose="info-note">
<div class="flex-shrink-0 pt-1">
<!-- Info Icon -->
<div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full border-2 border-blue-500 flex items-center justify-center">
<span class="text-blue-500 font-bold text-xs italic">i</span>
</div>
</div>
<p class="text-xs text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
<span class="font-bold">Lưu ý quan trọng:</span> Tiền sẽ được hoàn về phương thức thanh toán ban đầu trong vòng 3-5 ngày làm việc tùy thuộc vào ngân hàng của bạn.
      </p>
</section>
<!-- END: Important Note -->
</main>
<!-- END: Main Content -->
<!-- BEGIN: Bottom Actions -->
<footer class="fixed-bottom" data-purpose="footer-actions">
<div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
<!-- Confirm Cancel Button -->
<button class="w-full bg-[#007aff] text-white font-semibold py-4 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center gap-2 active:opacity-90 transition-opacity">
<div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full border-2 border-white flex items-center justify-center">
<svg class="h-3 w-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewbox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
<path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3"></path>
</svg>
</div>
<span>Xác nhận hủy</span>
</button>
<!-- Back Button -->
<button class="w-full bg-[#e9e9eb] text-gray-800 font-semibold py-4 rounded-xl active:opacity-90 transition-opacity">
        Quay lại
      </button>
</div>
</footer>
<!-- END: Bottom Actions -->
</body></html>